keywords = {Artificial intelligence ; Classification ; Data analysis ; Data mining ; Decision making ; Digital Elevation Models ; Digital imaging ; Elevation ; Flood hazards ; Flood mapping ; Flood predictions ; Flood Risk Mapping ; Floods ; Flow velocity ; Geographic information systems ; Geographical information systems ; Google Earth Engine ; Imagery ; Information systems ; Land use ; Landsat ; Landsat satellites ; Learning algorithms ; Machine learning ; Mapping ; Methods ; Mountains ; Normalized difference vegetative index ; Precipitation ; Radar ; Random Forest ; Remote Sensing ; Risk ; Risk assessment ; River basins ; Rivers ; Satellite imagery ; Satellites ; Software ; Soil density ; Soil properties ; Soil texture ; Spaceborne remote sensing ; Texture ; Topography ; Urban areas ; Waterways},
